title: Newly Renovated 3 Bedroom/3 Bath With Panoramic Views !!!!!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
